        <title>Graduating my First Class: Intro To SE</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I taught my very first class this past June in front of 13 teenagers who, much like myself, had no idea what they were getting themselves into.  &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


